{"prompt": "Build a user-friendly site for a pet grooming salon. The design should prominently display a cheerful light pink.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Pawsitively Pampered Pet Grooming</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #FFD1DC; /* Cheerful light pink */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #FFB6C1; /* Slightly darker pink for contrast */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #FF69B4; /* A brighter pink accent */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #FFC0CB; /* Another shade of pink */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #FF69B4;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .hero img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 5px solid #FF69B4;\n        }\n        .services ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .services li {\n            background-color: #FFF0F5; /* Very light pink */\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #FFB6C1;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #FF69B4; /* Bright pink for call to action */\n            color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .cta button {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #FF69B4;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta button:hover {\n            background-color: #FFB6C1;\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: #FFD1DC;\n            color: #333;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Pawsitively Pampered Pet Grooming</h1>\n        <p>Where every pet is treated like royalty!</p>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/800x400/FFC0CB/FFFFFF?text=Happy+Pups+Grooming\" alt=\"A happy dog getting groomed\">\n            <h2>Give Your Furry Friend the Best Care</h2>\n            <p>We offer a full range of grooming services to keep your pets looking and feeling their best.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Our Salon</h2>